    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292790/extras/5ebf93f122d31105d7cffdd2f2b9bfd7.avif?t=1694639349\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>欢迎来到 For The Motherland，这是一款第一人称恐怖游戏，发生在陷入混乱的苏联空间站上。玩家将体验被困在太空中的恐惧和孤立，因为他们穿过空间站并揭开倒塌背后的真相。<br><br>在游戏中，玩家可以选择通过多种游戏模式进行游戏，每种模式都会讲述一个关于空间站倒塌的不同短篇故事。从进行实验的科学家的角度，到试图在致命病毒爆发中生存的船员，玩家将体验到各种各样的可怕场景。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292790/extras/f6f5923d01e728b91f42827ee13f983e.poster.avif?t=1694639349\" width=564 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292790/extras/f6f5923d01e728b91f42827ee13f983e.webm?t=1694639349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292790/extras/f6f5923d01e728b91f42827ee13f983e.mp4?t=1694639349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>当玩家探索空间站时，他们会遇到各种各样的敌人，包括变异生物和故障机器人。为了生存，玩家将需要使用隐身和解决问题的技能来避免被发现并找到逃离车站的方法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292790/extras/0bf083b1dd099a8bb595abe50416e0af.poster.avif?t=1694639349\" width=564 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292790/extras/0bf083b1dd099a8bb595abe50416e0af.webm?t=1694639349\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292790/extras/0bf083b1dd099a8bb595abe50416e0af.mp4?t=1694639349\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>For The Motherland 提供独特且身临其境的恐怖体验，玩家在严酷的太空环境中为生存而战，解开空间站倒塌的谜团。凭借其激烈的游戏玩法和令人毛骨悚然的氛围，For The Motherland 是恐怖游戏（如 IT STEALS 和其他独立经典游戏）粉丝的必玩游戏。",
